{
 "name": "RPlog_Nodes_on_the_Web",
 "title": "Nodes on the Web",
 "summary": "Drawn through the dark streets of an ancient city, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios seeks out Luke Skywalker in the torchlit temple of Casohav, troubled by her sense of responsibility for the fallen Selas, Simon Sezirok, whom she fears her influence helped pull deeper into darkness. She wonders whether she should try to redeem him as Luke once redeemed his own father. Finding Luke standing beneath the temple's grim engravings of Death, she calls out to him, and the Jedi Master, a beacon in the Force, gently receives her and asks if she feels what he feels. Their meeting opens a quiet meditation on belief, struggle, and the threads of the Force that connect them.",
